entry.title: Welcome
entry.content:
Welcome to Endless Venture

January 09, 2018 · Camilla Yan

Welcome to Endless Venture. A place full of enthralling adnventures, tech-related wonders, unbeknowst designers and incessant ramblings; proudly brought to you by a 21 year old university student born and raised in Melbourne, Australia.


Creating this website is, perhaps, more for my sanity than for practising my web development skills, as I feel if I don't write down everything that's raging inside my head, my brain will surely and undoubtly explode.


Feel free to email me, and I welcome you all to join me on my endless venture...
